The field is currently operated by [[Türkmengaz]]<ref> {{cite news |url= http://finance.rambler.ru/news/oil/58352775.html |script-title=ru:В Туркменистане запускают трубу в Китай |trans-title=A pipeline to China is started in Turkmenistan |publisher= Rambler.ru. Finance |date= 2009-12-14 |accessdate=2010-01-07|language= Russian }} </ref> Production from Malai field contributes to the overall volume of gas transported via [[Turkmenistan-China gas pipeline]].<ref> {{cite news |url= http://www.projectstoday.com/Potpourri/MiddleEast/Turkmenia-China%20pipeline%20to%20be%20ready%20by%20end-2009.asp |title= Turkmenia-China pipeline to be ready by end-2009 |publisher= Projects Today |date= 2009-04-11 |accessdate=2010-01-07}} </ref>
